      • builtFileWithResponse

        public static BuiltFile builtFileWithResponse(JSONObject jsonObject)
        Returns BuiltFile instance to download image or file. If JSON object is not appropriate then it will return null.
        Parameters:
        jsonObject - json object of particular file attached in the built object.
        BuiltFile can be generate using of data filled BuiltObject and builtFileWithResponse(JSONObject).
        1. Single Attachment :-
            BuiltFile builtFile = BuiltFile.builtFileWithResponse(builtObject.getJSONObject(Attach_Image_Field_Uid));
        2. Multiple Attachment :-
                  
    JSONArray array = builtObject.getJSONArray(Attach_Image_Field_Uid);                 
    for (int i = 0; i < array.length(); i++) {
  
           BuiltFile builtFile = BuiltFile.builtFileWithResponse(builtObject.getJSONObject(Attach_Image_Field_Uid));
    }
        Returns:
        BuiltFile instance.
